          "reviewBody": "My niece studying in this school.\nShe is telling that teachers are taking class room session very less . Due to lack of teachers. Teachers taking classes for multiple branches for 1 week,Those teacher taking classes for padappai vellamal branch and guduvanchery branch.\nEnglish science and maths teacher taking classes for 4 classes only per week.teachers not clarifying the student doubt’s properly. But the school fees above 70000 rs per year.",
