            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm studying into his school since the very start and it was a good experience in the beginning but before covid it started going downhill bad staff and bad vp. All the 5 star reviews are from the teachers or staff. The VP is blackmailing my family because we asked for leave and other things he hates everyone. I want to take this to the head office of this school. Please dont join your kids here it's a waste of money and staff are really bad and rude they just want money and the higher ups like the principal and vp or ACO don't care about anything.. The campus language is supposed to be English but I have never seen a single staff speaking English and they have a different opinion when there's a parent around and go rude just after they leave it's almost as if they're trying to make a fool out of us. Worst school of this group I happy to leave this year.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
