          "reviewBody": "My daughter joined in this school at Jkg, now she is in Grade 1. She learned lot of things in past two years, she gained her knowledge. From Jkg( Katherine mam), to Skg( Sangeetha mam) both of them take care very well. Her teacher's teach the good activities, like don't eat the junk foods. In this school teachers take care each student personally.",
