          "reviewBody": "My son was studing in VVG from junior Kg and now he is into 1st standard. I can see a huge growth in these 2 years. He has learned a lot of new words at this age. They focus not only on studies they encourage each kid to participate in all other activities like sports, arts. I am so surprised to see him asking lot of curious questions. Similarly they encourage kids to eat healthy food at home and school. After joining this school I see my son has changed his food habits.",
